        <h3 class="mt-12 text-pretty text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl lg:text-balance">Leading Transformation</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base/7 text-gray-600">The cognii approach centers around the process described in the book <span class="font-semibold">Leading Transformation - How to Take Charge of Your Company's Future (Harvard Business Review Press, 2018)</span> written by Thomas together with Nathan Furr and Kyle Nel.</p>
