            Envisioning the Future
          </dt>
          <dd>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base/7 text-gray-600">Stories are one of humankind's oldest and most powerful tools. We use it to combat narrow thinking and the inate human habit of focussing on only incremental improvements to the status quo.</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base/7 text-gray-600">Latest neuroscience research reveals that stories release a rush of neurochemicals that can literally sync people's brain and motivate action. We use this to create a strategic narrative and radically reenvision what is possible using speculative fiction and visual mediums (e.g. comic book).</p>
